						<div class="postbody">You need to set Max and TV Aspect while you're already in Fullscreen mode. If you do it while in Windowed mode, the settings apply to Windowed mode.<br /><br />Switch to Fullscreen, and hit Escape. You should be able to use the menu and access the settings for Fullscreen mode.<br /><br />I didn't find this intuitive. I don't normally expect the settings in the menu to only apply to the current context, but that's how it's done in Nestopia, I guess.</div>

